{"msg":{"practice":[{"id":182,"question":"笔记本电脑与传统台式电脑相比，体现了SCAMPER中的哪些思维？","type":2,"analysis":"Substitute 触控板代替鼠标等<br/>Combine 将传统台式机的主机、显示器、键盘融合到一台设备上<br/>Adapt 可应用于移动办公的场景<br/>SCAMPER是从产品和服务改进者的视角去运用的。需要从创新思考的起点，而非创新的结果去理解。","pic":null,"difficulty":3,"knowledgeId":15,"sceneId":1,"del":false,"problemId":3,"sequence":1,"example":true,"practiceUid":"T003C002F004L01001","score":50,"choiceList":[{"id":552,"questionId":182,"subject":"Substitute替代","sequence":1,"isRight":true,"selected":false},{"id":553,"questionId":182,"subject":"Combine合并","sequence":2,"isRight":true,"selected":false},{"id":554,"questionId":182,"subject":"Adapt适应","sequence":3,"isRight":true,"selected":false},{"id":555,"questionId":182,"subject":"Modify修改","sequence":4,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":556,"questionId":182,"subject":"Put to other uses改作他用","sequence":5,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":557,"questionId":182,"subject":"Eliminate消除","sequence":6,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":558,"questionId":182,"subject":"Reverse逆向","sequence":7,"isRight":false,"selected":false}],"discussList":[{"id":1910,"warmupPracticeId":182,"repliedId":null,"comment":"除了E都选了，M修改，外形变化；E减化，去掉了很多大部头零件，实现轻便；R反向，台式电脑的弊端，笨重无法移动，所以有了这样的发明。感觉都说得通啊。","openid":null,"addTime":1491820815000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"JO","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyibbafiaiamMCT1NibWJvqonUP8wpgyMv9VFbibW13z23eLGopaoFebhOC3eueQYWpbuP5Oz15Az5R3JY/0","discussTime":"2017-04-10"},{"id":1377,"warmupPracticeId":182,"repliedId":null,"comment":"非常不理解为什么不满足M和E，产品的形状明明是有了很大改观的，也做到了简化，比如把主机那么庞大的东西整合到笔记本那么小的地方重新排序安装","openid":null,"addTime":1490447694000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"文","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEuUJBibwaegwqwa7rXILx7WPapDW7tTnawmINtpCLZRonooMm0ezL1xuuMLrs1trOmgp0gmOpYOuk/0","discussTime":"2017-03-25"},{"id":1064,"warmupPracticeId":1